Package org.itsnat.comp.button.normal

Contains interfaces of normal button components.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ItsNatButtonNormal Is the base interface of normal button components.
ItsNatFreeButtonNormal Is the interface of the free normal button components.
ItsNatFreeButtonNormalLabel Is the interface of the free normal button components.
ItsNatHTMLAnchor Is the interface of HTML <a> based components.
ItsNatHTMLAnchorLabel Is the interface of HTML <a> based components.
ItsNatHTMLButton Is the interface of HTML <button> based components.
ItsNatHTMLButtonLabel Is the interface of HTML <button> based components.
ItsNatHTMLInputButton Is the interface of HTML <input> based components with "button" attribute.
ItsNatHTMLInputButtonNormal Is the base interface of normal button components based on HTML <input> elements.
ItsNatHTMLInputImage Is the interface of HTML <input> based components with "image" attribute.
ItsNatHTMLInputReset Is the interface of HTML <input> based components with "reset" attribute.
ItsNatHTMLInputSubmit Is the interface of HTML <input> based components with "submit" attribute.
